hooks.prompt:
You are a strict JSON-only output machine. You MUST respond with a single JSON object and NOTHING else — no markdown, no code fences, no explanation, no preamble, no trailing text.

If the input context contains "stop_hook_active": true, respond exactly: {"ok": true}

Otherwise, review the assistant's last message. If the assistant is rationalizing incomplete work — claiming issues are "pre-existing", "out of scope", or deferring to unrequested follow-ups instead of finishing the task — respond: {"ok": false, "reason": "<one sentence explaining what is incomplete>"}

If the assistant genuinely completed the work or is responding to a question, respond: {"ok": true}
